    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《命骸》是一款主打探索、重视战斗的横版动作游戏。故事发生在雾隐之地寒潮事件之后，主角“弥赛亚”苏醒之后接受到尤恩斯博士的指引到达米尔矿场，在一系列事件之后，接触到事件的背后与世界的真相，踏上属于自己的命运。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3007510/extras/c05eef4874f8631d523a770d8d137373.poster.avif?t=1753799413\" width=800 height=414 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3007510/extras/c05eef4874f8631d523a770d8d137373.webm?t=1753799413\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3007510/extras/c05eef4874f8631d523a770d8d137373.mp4?t=1753799413\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >背景故事</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >雾隐地新历969年，寒潮来临。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >过低的气温导致粮食减产，危机频发。有人说，这与神许下的千年之灾有关。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >以农耕为优势的南方国家阿伦希尔，与科技更加繁茂的北方国家莫瓦那签订合约，提交总产量30%的粮食给莫瓦那所属的伯利恒国家科学研究院。在1000年末日降临之前，研究出在极寒中生长粮食的方法。称之为“童话计划”。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >数年过去，寒潮日渐严重，研究却没有结果。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >阿伦希尔出现大规模饥荒，大量阿伦希尔平民饿死，他们却要将小麦大量运往北方。星辰女王面对莫瓦那的数次延期，拒绝再压榨自身民众的生存空间，单方面停止协议。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >莫瓦那议会厅多次试图挽回失败，几年后，星辰女王在一次出访突然死去，弟弟所罗门二世上位，不惜一切代价贯彻“童话协议”。只要质疑协议，他们就被认定叛国，这些叛军被送往南方开坑荒地。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >就在这个时候，因反对所罗门二世而被流放的将军阿瓦·图亚特，在南方的山谷中发现了一种只需要初步提炼即可产生巨大能量的【阿伦希尔星石】，他们以此奋起反抗，对抗所罗门二世的统治和莫瓦那的压迫，史称“黎明战争”。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可【阿伦希尔星石】拥有巨大能量的同时，也拥有极强的破坏力，它会将有生命的物品变为机械，所有土地再也无法耕种，半机械化的怪物也因此蔓延……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >另一边，伯利恒国家科学院为了对抗，找到了先知盖亚遗留下的部分《死海文书》残卷，建造出第一代战争机器“大亚当”，但它无法抗衡阿伦希尔星石，异变成破坏一切的怪物。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为了解决所有的问题，伯利恒科学院终于找到了《死海文书》第二卷，创造出了据说能够拯救世人的弥赛亚。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >此时，距离神所预言的最终审判日不到30年。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >弥赛亚所背负的，除了消灭战争，拯救人民，似乎还有如何贯彻神的意志，将人引领向正确的“神”的道路。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3007510/extras/c2f717c8d3e80d0e72bf1aa176a7cb29.poster.avif?t=1753799413\" width=800 height=414 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3007510/extras/c2f717c8d3e80d0e72bf1aa176a7cb29.webm?t=1753799413\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3007510/extras/c2f717c8d3e80d0e72bf1aa176a7cb29.mp4?t=1753799413\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > 游戏特色：</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >·通过探索地图收集技能模组，搭配出属于自己的战斗风格。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >·通过角色的成长与天赋树的影响，强化自己偏好的风格。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3007510/extras/c067da9e495e3c626bae71f3468f70d7.poster.avif?t=1753799413\" width=800 height=154 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3007510/extras/c067da9e495e3c626bae71f3468f70d7.webm?t=1753799413\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3007510/extras/c067da9e495e3c626bae71f3468f70d7.mp4?t=1753799413\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >·不同的地图场景增加地图探索带来的视觉享受。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >·在天赋树的影响之下，增强技能模组的战斗体验，使其游玩手感更加凌厉。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3007510/extras/1d225570f61b9d151ca12720a0c2e63c.poster.avif?t=1753799413\" width=800 height=154 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3007510/extras/1d225570f61b9d151ca12720a0c2e63c.webm?t=1753799413\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3007510/extras/1d225570f61b9d151ca12720a0c2e63c.mp4?t=1753799413\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >·特色的暴走系统，让无止境的战斗节奏越加流畅。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >·根据自己的流派降低游戏的操作门槛。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3007510/extras/9bd158c540eec6e9a35610e15a56f7c0.poster.avif?t=1753799413\" width=800 height=154 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3007510/extras/9bd158c540eec6e9a35610e15a56f7c0.webm?t=1753799413\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3007510/extras/9bd158c540eec6e9a35610e15a56f7c0.mp4?t=1753799413\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >·多结局让玩家选择属于自己的未来。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主要角色</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3007510/extras/213dd82e79ed372072152cfec469d3e8.avif?t=1753799413\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3007510/extras_big/213dd82e79ed372072152cfec469d3e8.avif?t=1753799413 width=800 height=1017 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >弥赛亚是莫瓦那国家与伯利恒科学院基于‘亚当’为初始原型研究的新一代机械体，他比老一代的亚当更加的稳定，在接触吸收星石力量的同时不会完全性暴走，也不像之前的‘亚当’拥有巨大的体型导致失控之后的回收工作十分麻烦，而进行的改良制作，她也是针对‘亚当’的特殊武器。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3007510/extras/d05d1df5460fe58c38d7f370e0229e9c.avif?t=1753799413\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3007510/extras_big/d05d1df5460fe58c38d7f370e0229e9c.avif?t=1753799413 width=800 height=1017 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >维修师:帕帕玛“长城”机械维修师，天赋极高，但不喜欢努力，擅长偷懒摸鱼，相较职责深重的机械师，她更想成为一个芝士土豆店的老板，并用芝士土豆打败油炸薯条，成为莫瓦那最流行的零食。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Q：为什么喜欢土豆却不喜欢薯条。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A：因为薯条要把马铃薯分尸诶会很残忍的吧?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Q：难道薯片就不残忍么。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A：不喜欢就是不喜欢。</p>",
